README.md

Awesome

   A curated list of resources for learning about application security.
   Contains books, websites, blog posts, and self-assessment quizzes.

   Maintained by [https://paragonie.com/]Paragon Initiative Enterprises
   with contributions from the application security and developer
   communities. We also have [https://paragonie.com/projects]other
   community projects which might be useful for tomorrow's application
   security experts.

   If you are an absolute beginner to the topic of software security, you
   may benefit from reading
   [https://paragonie.com/blog/2015/08/gentle-introduction-application-sec
   urity]A Gentle Introduction to Application Security.

Contributing

   
   Please refer to the contributing guide for details.

