C

Books and ebooks

SEI CERT C Coding Standard (2006)

   Released: May 24, 2006

   A community-maintained Wiki detailing secure coding standards for C
   programming.

Defensive Coding: A Guide to Improving Software Security by the Fedora Security Team (2018)

   Released: March 10, 2018

   Provides guidelines for improving software security through secure
   coding. Covers common programming languages and libraries, and focuses
   on concrete recommendations.

