   Security Project

Security Training from BinaryMist

   We run many types of info-sec security training, covering Physical,
   People, VPS, Networs, Cloud, Web Applications. Most of the content is
   sourced from the
   [https://leanpub.com/b/holisticinfosecforwebdevelopers]book series Kim
   has been working on for several years. More info can be found
